{"id":258624,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-上海维权人士陈建芳等人到北京最高法院/","date":"2012-10-23T02:45:57Z","modified":"2012-10-23T02:45:57Z","title":"维权网 | 上海维权人士陈建芳等人到北京最高法院要求诉权（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>，上海上访维权人士李雪美、谢金华、陈建芳等人到达北京继续举报控告，揭发腐败，并要求最高法院依法保障公民的诉权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日</span><span>上午，李雪美、谢金华、陈建芳、张淑芝到北京最高法院要求立案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海市宝山区高境镇江杨村孟家宅</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">95</span><span>号李雪美，原拥有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">282</span><span>平方米</span><span>的私房于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2001</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>遭到宝山区政府非法暴力强制拆迁，至今得不到解决。被刑事拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>天（诉讼至法院，既不立案，也不裁定）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>谢金华原有私房</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">387</span><span>平方米</span><span>，阁楼</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">80</span><span>平方米</span><span>（高度为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1.8</span><span>米</span><span>），还有约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">166</span><span>平方米</span><span>没有得到安置。承包集体土地所有权、宅基地、自留地约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>亩未得到补偿。被行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>次、刑事拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>次、取保候审</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>次（诉讼至法院，既不立案，也不裁定）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陈建芳原居住地（户籍所在地）上海市浦东新区航头镇沉香村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">460</span><span>号，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2005</span><span>年航头镇沉香村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">150</span><span>公顷</span><span>农村集体土地被政府有关部门非法征收，拆迁农村宅基地上的私房不依法给予补偿安置。陈建芳举报控告，被打成轻伤、行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>次、刑事拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>次、取保候审</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>次、劳动教养一年三个月，多次被关黑监狱（诉讼至法院，既不立案，也不裁定）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>黑龙江省望奎县上访维权人士癌症患者张淑芝在治病途中被望奎县信访局副局长姜海军和公安局一位姓黄的女警察抢走财物，还把张淑芝劳动教养一年，行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>次（诉讼至法院和检察院，既不立案，也不裁定）。张淑芝依法维权，由于地方政府行政乱作为，多次无故关押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家到最高法院要求立案，希望最高法院能依法监督地方法院的不作为及枉法渎职，依法保障公民的诉权，以彰显法律的公正。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-KL-u33wUvFA/UIX0SYGTc4I/AAAAAAAARx0/MiWSZi9PH_g/s1600/%E5%BC%A0%E6%B7%91%E8%8A%9D%E3%80%81%E6%9D%8E%E9%9B%AA%E7%BE%8E%E3%80%81%E9%99%88%E5%BB%BA%E8%8A%B3.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"235\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-KL-u33wUvFA/UIX0SYGTc4I/AAAAAAAARx0/MiWSZi9PH_g/s320/%E5%BC%A0%E6%B7%91%E8%8A%9D%E3%80%81%E6%9D%8E%E9%9B%AA%E7%BE%8E%E3%80%81%E9%99%88%E5%BB%BA%E8%8A%B3.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>左起：张淑芝、李雪美、陈建芳</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-5Omr2JFZl7E/UIX0XSJTpaI/AAAAAAAARx8/MBMIII_iDSg/s1600/%E9%99%88%E5%BB%BA%E8%8A%B3%EF%BC%88%E5%B7%A6%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E8%B0%A2%E9%87%91%E5%8D%8E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E6%9D%8E%E9%9B%AA%E7%BE%8E%EF%BC%88%E5%8F%B3%EF%BC%89DSCI1513.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"258\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-5Omr2JFZl7E/UIX0XSJTpaI/AAAAAAAARx8/MBMIII_iDSg/s320/%E9%99%88%E5%BB%BA%E8%8A%B3%EF%BC%88%E5%B7%A6%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E8%B0%A2%E9%87%91%E5%8D%8E%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%AD%EF%BC%89%E3%80%81%E6%9D%8E%E9%9B%AA%E7%BE%8E%EF%BC%88%E5%8F%B3%EF%BC%89DSCI1513.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>左起：陈建芳、谢金华、李雪美</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\